QuestData.Title: Work Order: Dominance Offensive I
QuestData.Description: <Yoon's writing decorates the page though his feelings seem conflicted.>$b$bI normally try to stay out of conflict, but an order is an order. Since you are of the Horde I decided to pass this order your way.$b$bThe Dominance Offensive has requested an order of red blossom leeks.$b$bThe troops down there just can't seem to get enough of them!
QuestData.LogDescription: Plant 8 Red Blossom Leek Seeds on Sunsong Ranch.
